thread.title: BRIEF-Fujian Sunnada Communication amends FY 2017 net profit outlook

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Fujian Sunnada Communication amends FY 2017 net profit outlook

organizations.name: reuters) - fujian sunnada communication co ltd

text:
Jan 30(Reuters) - Fujian Sunnada Communication Co Ltd :
* Says net profit for FY 2017 to be 2 million yuan to 10 million yuan
* Says in the previous outlook, the company expected the net profit for FY 2017 to be 10 million yuan to 20 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 105.4 million yuan
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/Az4Eod
